  "doc_id": "38326",
  "text": "We assembled a wide range of regulatory interactions in the course of the analysis on the data sets above. As validation for the MARA predicted transcriptional regulatory interactions, we compiled a list of genes responding to siRNA perturbation experiments and a list of genes bound by transcription factors based on our experiments above as well as other publicly available large-scale experiments. Furthermore, we screened over 1000 publications to extract 440 manually curated regulatory interactions between regulators where we required that the interactions were validated with EMSA or ChIP in human cells. We provide the corresponding Pubmed IDs as evidence for the interaction. We obtained ElMMo (23) miRNA target predictions from the MirZ web server [CITATION_1] and complemented with genes responding to our miRNA over expression described above.",
